snippet.title: 【Kiichan】this is what falling in love feels like (Multilingual Full Version)
snippet.description:
"No words can express the feeling I get just by being with you"
_______________________________________
STREAM → https://distrokid.com/hyperfollow/kitsuiakira/this-is-what-falling-in-love-feels-like-multilingual

Merry Christmas everyone !!!

It's been such a wild year, and I am fully aware that many of you have been requesting a full version of this song, so here is my Christmas gift for all of you! I hope it meets your expectations, I put a lot of love & time into it ;w;

Super thank you to mr. foxxo Reynard Blanc for the beautiful music as always!!

And super thank you to YOU too, for being here & supporting me & my content! There will definitely be a lot more coming in the next few days, as well as next year and hopefully many more years after that!! This is truly what falling in love feels like, and it's me being spoiled by you guys so much, so you deserve the same back!
